Vendors are utilizing protocols with UDP to enable NAT. 
  AS ICMP can NAT out of network so can UDP. 

Suports Unicast, Broadcast & multicast. 
Protocols that use UDP: DNS,SNMP,DHCP,NFS,TFTP 
Header is a psuedo-header check which includes IP header
Checksum optional in IPv4 mandatory in IPv6. 
Traceroute in linux uses UDP
Length 0 in jumbogram for IPv6
